{"id":841,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":841,"title":"Ezekiel 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel reproves false prophets, both male and female, who speak lies, to whom God has not spoken."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.1","order":"02.27.013.55731"},["b","1"],"And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.2","order":"02.27.013.55732"},["b","2"],"Son of man, prophesy against the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"prophets"],"of Israel that prophesy, and say thou unto them that prophesy out of their own hearts, Hear ye the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],";"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.3","order":"02.27.013.55733"},["b","3"],"Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Woe unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"foolish"],"prophets, that follow their own spirit, and have seen nothing!"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.4","order":"02.27.013.55734"},["b","4"],"O Israel, thy prophets are like the foxes in the deserts."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.5","order":"02.27.013.55735"},["b","5"],"Ye have not gone up into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"gaps"],", neither made up the hedge for the house of Israel to stand in the battle in the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.6","order":"02.27.013.55736"},["b","6"],"They have seen vanity and lying",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"divination"],", saying, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"saith: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath not sent them: and they have made",["i","others"],"to hope that they would confirm the word."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.7","order":"02.27.013.55737"},["b","7"],"Have ye not seen a vain vision, and have ye not spoken a lying divination, whereas ye say, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"saith",["i","it;"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"albeit"],"I have not spoken?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.8","order":"02.27.013.55738"},["b","8"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Because ye have spoken",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"vanity"],", and seen",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"lies"],", therefore, behold, I",["i","am"],"against you, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.9","order":"02.27.013.55739"},["b","9"],"And mine hand shall be upon the prophets that see vanity, and that divine lies: they shall not be in the assembly of my people, neither shall they be written in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"writing"],"of the house of Israel, neither shall they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"enter"],"into the land of Israel; and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.10","order":"02.27.013.55740"},["b","10"],"¶Because, even because they have seduced my people, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Peace"],"; and",["i","there was"],"no peace; and one built up a wall, and, lo, others daubed it with untempered",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"mortar"],":"]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.11","order":"02.27.013.55741"},["b","11"],"Say unto them which daub",["i","it"],"with untempered",["i","mortar,"],"that it shall fall: there shall be an overflowing shower; and ye, O great hailstones, shall fall; and a stormy wind shall rend",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.12","order":"02.27.013.55742"},["b","12"],"Lo, when the wall is fallen, shall it not be said unto you, Where",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"daubing"],"wherewith ye have daubed",["i","it?"]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.13","order":"02.27.013.55743"},["b","13"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; I will even rend",["i","it"],"with a stormy wind in my fury; and there shall be an overflowing shower in mine anger, and great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"hailstones"],"in",["i","my"],"fury to consume",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.14","order":"02.27.013.55744"},["b","14"],"So will I break down the wall that ye have daubed with untempered",["i","mortar,"],"and bring it down to the ground, so that the foundation thereof shall be discovered, and it shall fall, and ye shall be consumed in the midst thereof: and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.15","order":"02.27.013.55745"},["b","15"],"Thus will I accomplish my wrath upon the wall, and upon them that have daubed it with untempered",["i","mortar,"],"and will say unto you, The wall",["i","is"],"no",["i","more,"],"neither they that daubed it;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.16","order":"02.27.013.55746"},["b","16"],["i","To wit,"],"the prophets of Israel which prophesy concerning Jerusalem, and which see visions of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"peace"],"for her, and",["i","there is"],"no peace, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.17","order":"02.27.013.55747"},["b","17"],"¶Likewise, thou son of man, set thy face against the daughters of thy people, which prophesy out of their own heart; and prophesy thou against them,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.18","order":"02.27.013.55748"},["b","18"],"And say, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Woe to the",["i","women"],"that sew",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"pillows to all armholes"],", and make kerchiefs upon the head of every stature to hunt souls! Will ye hunt the souls of my people, and will ye save the souls alive",["i","that come"],"unto you?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.19","order":"02.27.013.55749"},["b","19"],"And will ye pollute me among my people for handfuls of barley and for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"pieces"],"of bread, to slay the souls that should not die, and to save the souls alive that should not live, by your lying to my people that hear",["i","your"],"lies?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.20","order":"02.27.013.55750"},["b","20"],"Wherefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Behold, I",["i","am"],"against your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"pillows"],", wherewith ye there hunt the souls to make",["i","them"],"fly, and I will tear them from your arms, and will let the souls go,",["i","even"],"the souls that ye hunt to make",["i","them"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"fly"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.21","order":"02.27.013.55751"},["b","21"],"Your kerchiefs also will I tear, and deliver my people out of your hand, and they shall be no more in your hand to be hunted; and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.22","order":"02.27.013.55752"},["b","22"],"Because with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"lies"],"ye have made the heart of the righteous sad, whom I have not made sad; and strengthened the hands of the wicked, that he should not return from his wicked way,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"by promising him life"],":"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.23","order":"02.27.013.55753"},["b","23"],"Therefore ye shall see no more vanity, nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"divine"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"divinations"],": for I will deliver my people out of your hand: and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.2a","order":"02.27.013.55754"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.3a","order":"02.27.013.55756"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.7.7-9"},"Hosea 9:7 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.9"},"2 Ne. 28:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.29"},"Hel. 13:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.5a","order":"02.27.013.55758"},["b","5a"],["span.small","IE"],"breaks in the wall."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.6a","order":"02.27.013.55760"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.7a","order":"02.27.013.55762"},["b","7a"],["span.small","OR"],"although."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.8a","order":"02.27.013.55764"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"folly."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.8b","order":"02.27.013.55766"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.9a","order":"02.27.013.55768"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-life"},"TG Book of Life"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-remembrance"},"Book of Remembrance"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/record-keeping"},"Record Keeping"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.9b","order":"02.27.013.55770"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.38"},"Ezek. 20:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.10a","order":"02.27.013.55772"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/28.9.8-9"},"Jer. 28:9 (8–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.10b","order":"02.27.013.55774"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.28"},"Ezek. 22:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.12a","order":"02.27.013.55776"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"plaster."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.13a","order":"02.27.013.55778"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/11.19"},"Rev. 11:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.21"},"16:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.6"},"Mosiah 12:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.16"},"D&C 29:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.16a","order":"02.27.013.55780"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.18a","order":"02.27.013.55782"},["b","18a"],["span.small","HEB"],"bands or coverings to all elbows (trappings for magical arts)."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.19a","order":"02.27.013.55784"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.21"},"Prov. 28:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.20a","order":"02.27.013.55786"},["b","20a"],["span.small","HEB"],"bands wherewith ye trap souls."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.20b","order":"02.27.013.55788"},["b","20b"],["span.small","HEB"],"free."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.22a","order":"02.27.013.55790"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-doctrine"},"TG False Doctrine"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.22b","order":"02.27.013.55792"},["b","22b"],["span.small","HEB"],"to save his life."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.23a","order":"02.27.013.55794"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/3.6"},"Micah 3:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.23b","order":"02.27.013.55796"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],"."]]}
